# Project rules

## Environment
- Project: `react`
- Framework: `tailwindcss`
- Markdown support: `next/mdx`

## App architecture and folder structure
- To keep things simple, all styling should exist in [globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css)
- Blog posts use app/posts/[slug]/page.tsx
- Content for blog posts are written in mdx markdown in app/content/posts
- Reused custom components should be defined in app/components
